name: Godskitchen Presents Clash Of The Gods
description:
The Angel Ascends. Godskitchen Returns.

After some time out for a rethink and a change, GK returns to Birmingham on Saturday 26th April to mark a new era in 2014!

In the first of some exciting new changes on the event, GK launches Clash Of The Gods in one of the UK’s most established, iconic and exciting event spaces, The Rainbow Warehouse, for the very first time.

The original back-to-back event concept and firm favourite amongst our GK community features over 40 artistes across 3 rooms, with 6 UK exclusive sets and 7 GK debut performances.

Already the fastest selling Godskitchen show, we've ever seen, with Early Bird tickets selling out in less than 2 minutes. Don't miss out on this land mark return!

Let battle commence!
